{"tid":554184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"切親手究竟要睇急診定門診","createTime":"2018-02-08T09:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T09:35:19.000Z","uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"302842b7468b279b1ee0b57c6285e000c58f722f","tid":554184,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"我啊媽切親手去咗廣華睇急診<br />\n我即刻飛的去倍佢<br />\n依家等左2個鐘都未開始處理傷口<br />\n雖然佢喺屋企用雲南白藥止咗血同用野求其包住傷口&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n總之去私院睇門診算&hellip;"},{"pid":"a9dfbe8df570c1b77a3f8f0ac748561d1dfa228f","tid":554184,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"263e72510f7cb3d19cced4d76967c3bb13510e0f","tid":554184,"uid":74911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"連診"},{"pid":"85af2c2895a53407746bbf8a445bfb155420de4c","tid":554184,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"睇門診肯定快過去急症室"},{"pid":"930fcc7d2c13c5937edc407004835e2b79b547b6","tid":554184,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"急症? 等得嚟傷口都埋咗口"},{"pid":"57d6cba325d5fc0dd5486e587985978e9045fd1e","tid":554184,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:16:58.000Z","msg":"其實自己止血消毒就得<br />\n<br />\n去急症排到佛誕都未到你"},{"pid":"354ed259ebed06401894a228d7f288ed9f272b4e","tid":554184,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"喺急症等幾個鐘真係人間煉獄<br />\n細個踢波咬柴唔識處理<br />\n又係去廣華<br />\n本身無咩事<br />\n等下等下發現腳踭越來越踵<br />\n到我果時已經踵到好似個棒球咁<br />\n仲等勁耐先好番<br />\n<br />\n如果我返屋企提起隻腳同用冰敷，晨早好番"},{"pid":"ee794814dc57a24b6be3068040f7f80d5c7dd7e6","tid":554184,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"睇家庭醫生"},{"pid":"6f19a25098eee496b762a6cbd32a9d8664a6560d","tid":554184,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"